00:32:04,600 --> 00:32:07,319
and then chews through
a live power line.

385
00:32:07,320 --> 00:32:09,999
- 1975, Marisol Chavez...
- Kaylie...

386
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:12,919
dies in her bedroom of
