1004
01:25:13,040 --> 01:25:14,466
(SHRIEKS)

1005
01:25:15,000 --> 01:25:16,950
(POUNDING ON DOOR)

1006
01:25:20,960 --> 01:25:22,959
(BOTH WHIMPERING)

1007
01:25:22,960 --> 01:25:25,342
(POUNDING CONTINUES)

1008
01:25:28,120 --> 01:25:31,026
(POUNDING CEASES)

1009
01:25:54,560 --> 01:25:56,703
We've got to get downstairs.

1010
01:25:57,400 --> 01:25:58,959
She's not gone.

1011
01:25:58,960 --> 01:26:00,879
- I'm gonna open the door.
- No!

1012
01:26:00,880 --> 01:26:04,519
I'm gonna open the door.
If she's not gone...

1013
01:26:04,520 --> 01:26:06,822
I want you to run right
down the stairs.

1014
01:26:07,800 --> 01:26:11,707
- What are you gonna do?
- Don't worry about that. Just run.

1015
01:26:16,320 --> 01:26:18,270
You ready?

1016
01:26:19,840 --> 01:26:24,702
I'm gonna open the door. You
run right down the stairs.

1017
01:26:26,720 --> 01:26:28,988
You trust me, right?

1018
01:26:30,760 --> 01:26:32,824
I trust you.

1019
01:26:37,120 --> 01:26:40,719
One... I love you.

1020
01:26:40,720 --> 01:26:43,944
Two... Straight for the stairs.

1021
01:26:47,000 --> 01:26:48,301
Three.

1022
01:26:51,800 --> 01:26:53,909
- (GRUNTING)
- (BOTH SHRIEK)

1023
01:27:16,000 --> 01:27:18,507
(GROANING)

1024
01:27:25,160 --> 01:27:27,349
(PANTING)

1025
01:28:05,320 --> 01:28:07,509
(WHISPERING) It's not real.

1026
01:28:16,520 --> 01:28:18,424
Just a trick.

1027
01:28:20,680 --> 01:28:22,630
You're gonna arrest me, Timbo?

1028
01:28:25,320 --> 01:28:26,667
(LOUD GUNSHOT)

1029
01:28:29,880 --> 01:28:31,830
Timbo?

1030
01:28:51,840 --> 01:28:53,505
Tim!

1031
01:28:56,920 --> 01:29:00,429
(FAINT WHISPERING)

1032
01:29:17,960 --> 01:29:19,466
(VOICE SHAKY) Tim?

1033
01:29:31,400 --> 01:29:33,862
(MOUTHING)

1034
01:29:35,880 --> 01:29:37,909
(SCREAMS)

1035
01:29:43,680 --> 01:29:46,267
(CRYING) Mommy, please, no.

1036
01:29:46,800 --> 01:29:49,341
(SCREAMING)

1037
01:30:20,000 --> 01:30:22,428
(GASPING, COUGHING)

1038
01:30:25,640 --> 01:30:27,180
(WHISPERING) Kaylie?

1039
01:30:28,760 --> 01:30:30,949
- Kaylie?
- (GUNSHOT)

1040
01:30:33,360 --> 01:30:34,900
Mommy!

1041
01:30:36,280 --> 01:30:38,025
Come on, Tim!

1042
01:30:38,840 --> 01:30:40,904
(SCREAMS)

1043
01:30:47,320 --> 01:30:49,439
(GASPING SOFTLY)

1044
01:30:49,440 --> 01:30:52,869
(INDISTINCT WHISPERS OVERLAPPING)

1045
01:31:56,080 --> 01:31:59,031
(BOTH GRUNTING)

1046
01:32:10,440 --> 01:32:14,439
It won't let us.

1047
01:32:14,440 --> 01:32:17,346
ALAN: I thought I told you
not to play around in here.

1048
01:32:27,560 --> 01:32:28,986
No.

1049
01:32:30,040 --> 01:32:32,104
This isn't you.

1050
01:32:33,000 --> 01:32:34,759
It is me.

1051
01:32:34,760 --> 01:32:35,959
(WHISPERS ECHOING)

1052
01:32:35,960 --> 01:32:38,799
I've met my demons,
and they are many.

1053
01:32:38,800 --> 01:32:40,559
WHISPERING VOICE: I've seen...

1054
01:32:40,560 --> 01:32:42,799
I've seen the devil...

1055
01:32:42,800 --> 01:32:44,239
WHISPERING VOICE: And he is...

1056
01:32:44,240 --> 01:32:45,951
and he is me.

1057
01:32:48,720 --> 01:32:50,465
(YELLING)

1058
01:32:52,640 --> 01:32:54,624
Dad!

1059
01:33:00,640 --> 01:33:02,510
Let her go!

1060
01:33:05,160 --> 01:33:07,462
(GASPING)

1061
01:33:43,280 --> 01:33:45,184
Run.

1062
01:33:48,480 --> 01:33:50,703
No! No!

1063
01:33:51,400 --> 01:33:52,799
Daddy!

1064
01:33:52,800 --> 01:33:55,199
(SOBBING)

1065
01:33:55,200 --> 01:33:56,706
Come on.

1066
01:34:01,320 --> 01:34:04,191
(BOTH WHIMPERING)

1067
01:34:09,200 --> 01:34:14,199
(TIMER BUZZING LOUDLY)

1068
01:34:14,200 --> 01:34:16,879
This isn't real! This isn't real!

1069
01:34:16,880 --> 01:34:18,864
This isn't real!

1070
01:34:20,280 --> 01:34:23,345
(BUZZING FADES)

1071
01:34:29,720 --> 01:34:31,749
Kaylie!

1072
01:34:34,000 --> 01:34:35,904
TIM: (DISTANT) Kaylie!

1073
01:34:44,840 --> 01:34:46,949
(SNIFFLING)

1074
01:34:48,280 --> 01:34:50,105
MARIE: Kaylie.

1075
01:35:00,680 --> 01:35:02,266
Mommy?

1076
01:35:06,520 --> 01:35:08,948
(TICKING)

1077
01:35:36,200 --> 01:35:38,468
(WET THUDDING)

1078
01:35:40,640 --> 01:35:42,988
(FAINT GURGLING)

1079
01:35:45,520 --> 01:35:48,471
(KAYLIE GAGGING)

1080
01:36:04,240 --> 01:36:07,066
KAYLIE: Tim. Tim look at me.

1081
01:36:08,840 --> 01:36:13,039
I want you to promise me, that
when we're big and we're strong,

1082
01:36:13,040 --> 01:36:15,519
we will make this right.

1083
01:36:15,520 --> 01:36:19,108
(DISTANT SIRENS APPROACHING)

1084
01:36:21,360 --> 01:36:23,742
We have to kill that thing.

1085
01:36:26,240 --> 01:36:28,508
For Mom and Dad.

1086
01:36:32,040 --> 01:36:34,308
I promise.

1087
01:36:45,880 --> 01:36:47,705
(STAMMERING) Kaylie?

1088
01:36:48,920 --> 01:36:50,745
Kaylie?

1089
01:36:52,400 --> 01:36:56,182
Kaylie! Kaylie! Kaylie!

1090
01:36:57,040 --> 01:37:02,079
Kaylie! Kaylie! Kaylie!

1091
01:37:02,080 --> 01:37:03,759
(SIRENS GROWING LOUDER)

1092
01:37:03,760 --> 01:37:06,347
(INDISTINCT RADIO CHATTER)

1093
01:37:34,680 --> 01:37:36,599
He called it in?

1094
01:37:36,600 --> 01:37:40,950
Yeah, he called 911,
and then he did this.

1095
01:37:47,040 --> 01:37:48,944
Where are you taking me?

1096
01:37:50,080 --> 01:37:52,279
No, it wasn't my fault!

1097
01:37:52,280 --> 01:37:54,479
- It was the mirror!
- Tim!

1098
01:37:54,480 --> 01:37:57,759
Wait! Stop! It wasn't me!

1099
01:37:57,760 --> 01:38:01,439
It wasn't me. It was the
mirror! It was the mirror!

1100
01:38:01,440 --> 01:38:03,359
Please! Please! You
have to believe me!

1101
01:38:03,360 --> 01:38:06,584
It was the mirror!
It was the mirror!

1102
01:38:08,560 --> 01:38:10,759
Please!

1103
01:38:10,760 --> 01:38:13,159
Hey! Hey!

1104
01:38:13,160 --> 01:38:14,759
KAYLIE: Don't forget!

1105
01:38:14,760 --> 01:38:16,903
Don't forget our promise!

1106
01:38:19,360 --> 01:38:21,344
Don't forget.

1107
01:38:32,960 --> 01:38:36,343
(SIREN WAILING)

1108
01:38:41,040 --> 01:38:44,184
(WHIMPERING)

1109
01:38:55,440 --> 01:39:00,507
(RADIO CHATTER FADES)

1110
01:39:59,600 --> 01:40:03,188
(HEART BEATING)

